channel.title: Who would like to join a project?
channel.description:
Hello people,
i am new to moparisthebest and i think its the first time ive ever posted on here i was always on the moparscape forums. anyway let me get to the point i was just wondering if anybody wanted to help create a runescape guide/help website and community. not just community i want it to be based on a/or round a website.
im just wondering who would be interested if there is anybody out there.
thanks for reading.
